    '<p>For this project, a local news outlet is defined as a news organization that demonstrates a commitment to accuracy/transparency, and is devoted primarily to reporting and publishing original news about local people, places, issues and events. Tell us about changes to local news outlets in your area including:'+

    '<ul><li>The closure, launch or merger of a news outlet (radio, television, online, or newspaper)</li>'+
